Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.45,0:00:10.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ふたりがきっと　出会えるような　魔法をかけて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.60,0:00:22.00,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,施展了倆人一定會相遇的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,両手をそっと　重ねてほら　ほほえむから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.75,0:00:29.10,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悄悄的合起雙手 你看 在微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとの気持ち　気付かないふりして
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.35,0:00:38.40,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的心情 卻當作沒有察覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然ふたり　恋に落ちたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.50,0:00:48.15,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然 倆人陷入了愛河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.20,0:00:53.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.50,0:01:01.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.70,0:01:08.40,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,だきしめたいのに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.85,0:01:17.60,OP1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很想擁抱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.10,0:01:22.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.20,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let Me Be With You
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.73,0:01:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.43,0:01:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然試了很多方法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.90,0:01:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但關於Chobits的資料\N卻大都是傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.71,0:01:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要 發牢騷能晚點再 發嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.81,0:01:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是，是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.38,0:01:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稔少爺，有郵件進來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一樣是來自之前的那個帳號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.38,0:01:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快打開來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.52,0:01:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.35,0:02:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#23         ちぃ，決定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.97,0:02:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,琴子，妳在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.17,0:02:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對於電腦的相關事項
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.11,0:02:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要 發生不正常動作\N或特殊狀況時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.41,0:02:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就要對其進行調查\N這就是我的程式設定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳被設定成那樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.05,0:02:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.18,0:02:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實絲茉茉也是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.22,0:02:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被設定成等待時要跳舞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.43,0:02:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.26,0:02:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棟公寓的線路有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.20,0:02:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下麻煩大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.63,0:02:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.33,0:02:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,緊急狀況啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.57,0:02:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這棟公寓使用了\N連大企業都用不到的超高速線路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.21,0:02:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.88,0:03:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現了， 發現了\N有不明物品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來確認這個不明物品吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.92,0:03:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.16,0:03:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.33,0:03:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（把我找出來         無人的小鎮）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.64,0:03:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾失去過很重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.74,0:03:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我曾有過一段悲傷的往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.92,0:03:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至今胸口仍會感到悲傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.45,0:03:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常非常悲傷的往事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.56,0:03:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明失去了重要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.99,0:03:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲傷的痛苦卻仍殘留著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.87,0:03:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是繼續的尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.00,0:03:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要繼續的尋找著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.61,0:04:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.94,0:04:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.21,0:04:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰寄來的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.72,0:04:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情形還不是很清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.29,0:04:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.35,0:04:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在搜尋連線資料後\N大概有個譜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.56,0:04:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是誰呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.49,0:04:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦的資料庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.33,0:04:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是柚姬之前入侵的電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.90,0:04:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,資料？\N那是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.57,0:04:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的電腦裡暗藏著\N某些很不得了的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.94,0:04:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連電腦界的帝王\N都想知道的秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，ちぃ她真的是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還不能確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.88,0:04:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但她應該是Chobits\N或是類似的特殊電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.15,0:04:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充滿謎團的神秘電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.89,0:04:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，真令人羨慕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.99,0:04:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那台電腦給你用\N真是太可惜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.56,0:04:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓一個完全不懂\N她有多麼棒的人擁有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.70,0:05:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟蹋寶物啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.54,0:05:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別一直叫她電腦電腦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.41,0:05:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的名字叫“ちぃ”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.94,0:05:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別把她叫的像物品一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.14,0:05:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.79,0:05:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始有動作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.56,0:05:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都給了那麼多提示了\N這也是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.77,0:05:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.17,0:05:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.17,0:05:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，戴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.67,0:05:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳對這個任務\N沒有感到疑問過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.48,0:05:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.88,0:05:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止會讓電腦\N陷入危機的程式啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.45,0:05:49.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算與倫理軟體相比較\N也沒有任何矛盾之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.28,0:05:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.52,0:05:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳知道當那位小姐啟動時\N會 發生什麼危險嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.03,0:05:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.83,0:06:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是儲存著所有電腦\N相關資訊的資料庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.07,0:06:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而妳是為了保護我\N而製造出來的防護軟體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.04,0:06:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人為了保護所有的電腦\N正打算阻止那位小姐的啟動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.88,0:06:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在啟動後究竟會 發生什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.75,0:06:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連是不是真的會有危險\N也一樣不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.59,0:06:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對那個“電腦之父”而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.53,0:06:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人型電腦全都像是\N他的親生子女般
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.53,0:06:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據我所記載的資料顯示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.43,0:06:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父母總是希望子女得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.17,0:06:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，那位小姐或許…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.57,0:06:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承繼著希望電腦也能得到幸福\N的這種意念也說不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.08,0:06:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說，所謂的危險是謊言嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.52,0:06:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.05,0:06:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.12,0:06:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電腦得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.12,0:07:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並不表示就能讓全人類得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.13,0:07:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.00,0:07:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很危險，所以要阻止她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.60,0:07:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.77,0:07:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.01,0:07:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.52,0:07:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白我只要做自己就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.45,0:07:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不需要與其他人比較
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.32,0:07:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，要加油喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.63,0:07:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.49,0:07:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長也請用功讀書喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.03,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.80,0:07:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.73,0:07:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.47,0:07:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.47,0:07:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然由我來講可能有點奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.84,0:07:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請好好珍惜ちぃ喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.35,0:07:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.52,0:08:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ真的是Chobits嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是如此\N我又該怎麼做才好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.56,0:08:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我真的能幫得上忙嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.20,0:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是喜歡自言自語啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.37,0:08:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.84,0:08:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.54,0:08:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都幫不了ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你傷得很深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過在那之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有件事得先搞清楚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.02,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.86,0:08:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我還不確定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.73,0:08:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，該說是掛念好呢\N還是擔心 …
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.13,0:08:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上電腦的男人\N真的會被瞧不起嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.34,0:08:57.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.04,0:09:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為，清水老師她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.51,0:09:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，的確
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.48,0:09:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我聽到她丈夫\N迷上電腦而捨棄她時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的很瞧不起那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.49,0:09:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過仔細想想\N我才 發現這是不一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不一樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.46,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倘若她丈夫迷上的不是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.23,0:09:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是別的女人的話\N那又會如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.67,0:09:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多香子就不會感到痛苦嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.10,0:09:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不會感到氣憤嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.47,0:09:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看不起的\N並非迷上電腦的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.18,0:09:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是抱著隨便的態度\N跟人或電腦交往的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.52,0:09:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.98,0:09:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不會告訴我\N你還喜歡其他女人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.95,0:09:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會阻止你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.03,0:10:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是我，我是那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.64,0:10:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.11,0:10:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我不是人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.61,0:10:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.35,0:10:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是我，所以他喜歡我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.62,0:10:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為他是他，所以才會喜歡上他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.02,0:10:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.03,0:10:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.70,0:10:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房間還是一樣什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.77,0:10:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗨，絲茉茉，過得好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.37,0:10:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的，絲茉茉今天也很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們兩人\N先跟新保出去一下好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.65,0:10:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.85,0:10:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看起來比本須和正常多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請多多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.49,0:10:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉我不正常喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.99,0:10:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聞雜人等先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.33,0:11:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人好好談談吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.03,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說要談談\N但該從何談起啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.36,0:11:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.50,0:11:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也不太明白\N自己是怎麼看待ちぃ的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，真的不知道嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.07,0:11:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是\N只是沒去想過而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.71,0:11:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.35,0:11:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有哪裡痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.58,0:11:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.29,0:12:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，你為什麼要抱ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.06,0:12:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.41,0:12:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉瑪！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？又有人入侵了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.44,0:12:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.84,0:12:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是資料的傳輸量太大…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.45,0:12:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，戴特，稍等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼啊，吉瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.52,0:12:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你的資料受損\N那該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.35,0:12:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算資料受損\N只要重新輸入不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.49,0:12:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是電腦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.73,0:12:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖說如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.83,0:12:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.83,0:12:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這附近
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.44,0:12:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那女孩就在這附近吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.47,0:12:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快點趕去才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.91,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要阻止那個程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.08,0:13:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被 發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.95,0:13:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我想讓那位小姐能夠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.40,0:13:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.14,0:13:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.82,0:13:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.79,0:13:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日比谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.13,0:13:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我有事想問妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.80,0:13:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.40,0:13:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全告訴你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.77,0:13:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,關於ちぃ的一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.11,0:14:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.01,0:14:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.58,0:14:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請往這邊走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這下面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.43,0:14:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我丈夫做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.00,0:14:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡，以及人型電腦的系統都是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.47,0:14:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.70,0:14:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼日比谷會有這個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.14,0:14:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道這個人是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.01,0:14:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.88,0:14:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相片中的人是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.58,0:14:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是在我們過去待過的\N研究所裡拍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.48,0:14:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我身旁的是“愛爾塔”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.89,0:14:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛爾塔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.39,0:14:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.22,0:14:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去名叫“愛爾塔”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.63,0:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在的名字則是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.06,0:14:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.40,0:14:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而另一個則是“芙蕾雅”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.87,0:15:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道這不是ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.61,0:15:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.61,0:15:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她們兩人是不同的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.28,0:15:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.91,0:15:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛爾塔與芙蕾雅\N是我丈夫為我製造的孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.69,0:15:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為無法生育的我所製造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.06,0:15:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的孩子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.59,0:15:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最先製造的是芙蕾雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我被叫到研究室去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.10,0:15:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她就在那裡\N睜開雙眼對著我笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.30,0:15:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.51,0:15:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.74,0:15:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在與我們一起的生活當中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.61,0:15:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢地學會了許多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.95,0:15:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可愛的成長著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.63,0:16:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫用盡他的愛與技術\N製造了芙蕾雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.40,0:16:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為的就是讓她能夠被愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.60,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及能夠愛上某人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.97,0:16:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照這些相片的人是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.64,0:16:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.04,0:16:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾雅得到了我們的愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.44,0:16:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並找到了自己所愛的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.85,0:16:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我們卻沒有 發現…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.25,0:16:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對方到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.46,0:16:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我因為擔心 沒精神的芙蕾雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.96,0:16:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是請我丈夫幫她做了個妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.40,0:16:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是愛爾塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.17,0:16:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.84,0:16:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了妹妹的芙蕾雅\N看起來好高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.01,0:16:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但有時還是會流露出\N憂鬱的表情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.55,0:16:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛上了一個人\N但卻又不得不放棄的痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.26,0:17:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天\N芙蕾雅無法忍受那種痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.89,0:17:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.53,0:17:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.30,0:17:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芙蕾雅所愛上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.21,0:17:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是我丈夫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.08,0:17:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然身邊的研究員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.38,0:17:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,建議將芙蕾雅的記憶消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我丈夫卻聽不進去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.29,0:17:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於是芙蕾雅決定讓自己消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.96,0:17:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過因為怕遺留下來的愛爾塔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.53,0:17:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也使用著同樣的系統
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.06,0:17:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害怕再次 發生此情況的研究員\N打算將愛爾塔處分掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.47,0:17:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我丈夫不同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.37,0:17:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久，我丈夫也病倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.68,0:17:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我將愛爾塔初始化後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.24,0:18:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望她能找到\N只屬於她的重要的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.48,0:18:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.02,0:18:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ對他們而言…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.09,0:18:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，對現在的電腦使用者而言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是非常危險的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.59,0:18:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危險？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.99,0:18:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,決定權在本須和…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.80,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.58,0:18:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,親愛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.08,0:18:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣做…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.81,0:18:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.08,0:18:37.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被這麼多人愛著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.72,0:18:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要愛上人卻不能得到幸福\N是很奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.52,0:18:46.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是電腦\N也應該有得到幸福的權利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.69,0:18:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的口頭禪對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.90,0:18:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了尋找電腦與人類的幸福\N你製造了ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.87,0:18:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.21,0:19:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會守護她到最後一刻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.61,0:19:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓ちぃ…得到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.45,0:19:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.35,0:19:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是妳，妳就是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.39,0:19:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.29,0:19:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我心 中只能容納一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.90,0:19:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他露出笑容\N我就會感到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.07,0:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他陪伴在我身旁\N我就會感到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.67,0:19:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.71,0:19:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要他感到幸福\N我就會感到幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.78,0:19:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與他人不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.75,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是特別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳找到了是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.62,0:19:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我那最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最特別的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.19,0:19:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只屬於我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.49,0:19:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他能找到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.83,0:19:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像我找到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.49,0:19:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後因為他是他\N所以才喜歡上他的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.43,0:20:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他能找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.57,0:20:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為是我才能辦到的事\N以及因為是我才辦不到的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.81,0:20:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在他 發現後，然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.35,0:20:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能因為我是我\N所以喜歡上我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.35,0:20:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從許多的人與那個之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.96,0:20:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他能找到我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.53,0:20:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望能喜歡上我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.83,0:20:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.70,0:20:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他沒找到的話…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.74,0:20:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.75,0:20:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.25,0:20:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.86,0:20:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.13,0:21:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是只屬於我的人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.70,0:21:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.50,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ喜歡秀樹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.64,0:21:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹喜歡ちぃ嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.94,0:21:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.22,0:21:26.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.12,0:21:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不營業真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.63,0:21:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聲音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.63,0:21:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.10,0:21:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚姬！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.44,0:21:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又聽到聲音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.14,0:21:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個…聲音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.38,0:21:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，妳們兩個怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.20,0:22:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.90,0:22:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚的街道如同深海般寂靜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.87,0:22:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,綿延的路上卻只有我孤獨一人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.05,0:22:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,循著遠方的聲音向前進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.16,0:23:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷找尋著一閃即逝的藍色光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:00.82,0:23:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要找到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.22,0:23:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後不再遺忘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.29,0:23:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使有多心 痛         也要在你身旁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.91,0:23:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到永遠         直到永遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:41.92,0:23:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個鎮上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.32,0:23:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有許多的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.06,0:23:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及許多的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.76,0:23:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,許多的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.30,0:23:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與許多的那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.90,0:23:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在許多地方一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.70,0:23:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上某人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.77,0:23:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被某人愛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.94,0:23:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從許多的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.94,0:24:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與那個之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.74,0:24:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.21,0:24:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits         下一回\N「只屬於ちぃ的人」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.12,0:24:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望那個人也能找到
